Class CommonDataSpecification

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.graph.metadata.DataSpecification
com.telenav.mesakit.graph.specifications.common.CommonDataSpecification

Direct Known Subclasses:
OsmDataSpecification
public class CommonDataSpecification extends DataSpecification
Data specification common to all data. Note that common factories, properties and attributes are inherited from DataSpecification. This is done to allow implementations to only override the parts they want to change.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
